{"id": "ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 147, "displayName": {"text": "Rice & Nori", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210SlVXeHZXRUpSWjA5V1VqbFJiMkkxUlVFM05VRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Love this place. I got the 3 hand roll set to go and it is fantastic. To go orders are packaged up very well. Everything is fresh and tastes amazing. I also tried their smoke scallop rice ball and it was delish. Highly recommend trying this place if you like handrolls and quick service.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love this place. I got the 3 hand roll set to go and it is fantastic. To go orders are packaged up very well. Everything is fresh and tastes amazing. I also tried their smoke scallop rice ball and it was delish. Highly recommend trying this place if you like handrolls and quick service.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Bianca Chu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116063257195720111371/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbjlKrttzbwtMxgEcHHuKZJBTEPYQyu_pB6Bxo4F5iq-MoiaHC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-21T22:21:58.353960200Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210SlVXeHZXRUpSWjA5V1VqbFJiMkkxUlVFM05VRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT210SlVXeHZXRUpSWjA5V1VqbFJiMkkxUlVFM05VRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c51ed1309ff9:0xa4ca9a0158d0cc59"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SmNFbFRNVXR1YlVGTVluSXRRMmt6Y0dscFRGRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great place for a quick bite to eat in or for take out. Their onigiris are FRESH!\n\nParking/Environment:\nThere’s a dedicated parking lot. On a Sunday early afternoon, it didn’t seem too packed but we just parked in the 10 minute spots since we only ordered take out. There were high and low seating indoors and some outdoor patio seats.\n\nFood:\nAside from their onigiris and hand rolls, they also sold Japanese snacks and drinks.\nWe ordered Spam & Egg Musubi ($4.25), Salmon Yuzu Miso ($4), Spicy Lobster Shrimp ($5.50), and Spicy Tuna Mayo ($4). They were sooo good and hit the spot! Wish I ordered more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great place for a quick bite to eat in or for take out. Their onigiris are FRESH!\n\nParking/Environment:\nThere’s a dedicated parking lot. On a Sunday early afternoon, it didn’t seem too packed but we just parked in the 10 minute spots since we only ordered take out. There were high and low seating indoors and some outdoor patio seats.\n\nFood:\nAside from their onigiris and hand rolls, they also sold Japanese snacks and drinks.\nWe ordered Spam & Egg Musubi ($4.25), Salmon Yuzu Miso ($4), Spicy Lobster Shrimp ($5.50), and Spicy Tuna Mayo ($4). They were sooo good and hit the spot! Wish I ordered more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Pauline Steele", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101060251691182206355/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMzafckkZEdoMMZqmOzrLW1fDcKrpPCFh6MWzpW6SeiebAhramMw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-07-13T00:21:56.537756132Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SmNFbFRNVXR1YlVGTVluSXRRMmt6Y0dscFRGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1SmNFbFRNVXR1YlVGTVluSXRRMmt6Y0dscFRGRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c51ed1309ff9:0xa4ca9a0158d0cc59"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MnV1RGZnEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I def recommend getting the 3 Handroll set for a filling lunch, very worth it as you get 3 handrolls (1 premium), your choice of sashimi, and edamame.\n\nI got the Spicy Eggplant Onigiri, Negi Toro Handroll, and Blue Crab Handroll. My favorites were the handrolls. I thought there was too much rice for the onigiri and it wasn’t spicy at all. The handrolls were pretty big and enjoyable.\n\nThe restaurant is bright and clean.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I def recommend getting the 3 Handroll set for a filling lunch, very worth it as you get 3 handrolls (1 premium), your choice of sashimi, and edamame.\n\nI got the Spicy Eggplant Onigiri, Negi Toro Handroll, and Blue Crab Handroll. My favorites were the handrolls. I thought there was too much rice for the onigiri and it wasn’t spicy at all. The handrolls were pretty big and enjoyable.\n\nThe restaurant is bright and clean.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Linda Lam", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112364136325478599619/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXflmPLdqmnZ-zfAdRPlJ9nSkdzth7Qny7GH7p0gnpwZBlsIJOx3g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-02-04T00:41:31.357481Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MnV1RGZnEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUR0MnV1RGZnEAE!2m1!1s0x80c2c51ed1309ff9:0xa4ca9a0158d0cc59"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURGMnNLbGpnRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Pretty nice spot here! We enjoyed the salmon handrolls, and salmon nigiri.  There is a parking lot, and some street parking. Cool interior with plenty of seating. There is also about 4 outdoor tables. Kid and dog friendly outside. Salmon was tasty, and everything was fresh. We also got the eggplant ohnigiri. That was solid, but mostly rice… staff was nice, and it was a fun spot for a quick bite! The menu was a bit confusing; the combo seemed higher pricing than the items individually.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Pretty nice spot here! We enjoyed the salmon handrolls, and salmon nigiri.  There is a parking lot, and some street parking. Cool interior with plenty of seating. There is also about 4 outdoor tables. Kid and dog friendly outside. Salmon was tasty, and everything was fresh. We also got the eggplant ohnigiri. That was solid, but mostly rice… staff was nice, and it was a fun spot for a quick bite! The menu was a bit confusing; the combo seemed higher pricing than the items individually.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "D. de Silva", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109833646263821366987/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUidSE4AhpJZDn1ilT4WI6fEuhqrVOwJ6TTdlL_D9u3fDAFD_k=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2023-11-06T01:50:42.942709Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURGMnNLbGpnRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURGMnNLbGpnRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c51ed1309ff9:0xa4ca9a0158d0cc59"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-Z8w0R7FwoARWczQWAGayqQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNeE9FcFNaWGR0VjNGa1ZHdzVOelk1WkVReWVHYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I am highly satisfied with my initial experience and anticipate returning. The service was prompt, the food was excellent, and it fully met expectations.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I am highly satisfied with my initial experience and anticipate returning. The service was prompt, the food was excellent, and it fully met expectations.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution